Get your questions answered by our technical team. You’ll get a live demo of MotherDuck’s data warehouse for analytics and see firsthand how our dual execution query engine delivers insanely interactive analytics for internal BI and customer-facing data applications.

### Best of all? It’s actually fun to use

- Get to production fast:Deliver data pipelines, production grade analytics, and ad-hoc datasets backed by DuckDB’s ultra-efficient, fast-improving query engine.

- Build with flexibility in mind:Optimize your workload’s underlying compute resources with 3 configurable instance types and a friendly UI that helps data engineers, developers, and non-technical analysts collaborate.

- Unite local + cloud workflows with dual execution:Develop locally and ship to production with the same database, unparalleled user ergonomics, and value-driven price for performance.
